<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Letter Book Copy: letters copied into a bound letter-book ]">LB</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>.
</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>The enclosure has not been identified.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-02-02-0096" class="document">GWs letter to Christopher Gist, 10 Oct. 1755</a>, authorizing him to form a company of scouts, and also especially, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-02-02-0324&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-02-02-0324-fn-0002#GEWN-02-02-02-0324-fn-0002" class="document">Adam Stephen to GW, 29 Mar. 1756 (second letter), n.2.</a></p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0209-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0210" class="document">GW to Robert Fell, this date.</a></p>

